com.example.colibris.calib

Class Meet2regress

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.colibris.calib.Meet2regress

  • public class Meet2regress
extends java.lang.Object
    This Meet2regress class is used when a meeting/calibration takes place. In particular, this class permits to handle the calibration. For this purpose, various type of regressions can be performed
